			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Staff Segment Quest</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=3524"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:dandelgado@csi.com">Sigurd - Cazic-Thule</a> | 
		                        12/11/1999 9:32:40 AM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">This is actually more of a request for information on a quest I never see listed anywhere.<BR>
<BR>
Without giving away the whole thing, in East Karanas you can attack of be attacked by something that drops a &quot;staff segment&quot; lore item and a key. The key is one of the bank strongbox keys in HighHold Keep that the banker tells you about. Give the key to the banker, she will give you an IDENTICALLY descriptioned &quot;staff segment&quot; ALSO a Lore Item (but obviously distinguishable).<BR>
<BR>
Here I and all the people I have asked are stuck. There is no one who GAVE me this quest, so I don't know what is next. Any clues would be appreciated.<BR>
<BR>
Sigurd - Cazic-Thule
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
			</td>
			</tr>
