	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				     Been working on this stumper for about 9 levels.  Couple things I found:  Fenn Kaesick soetimes is standing on the roof of the keep.  If you hail him he says something about being the exterminator.  Asking Jail Clerk Meryl &quot;who is fenn&quot; provoked a response about how he was imprisoned with a high elf in the dungeons until he was bailed out.  Talking to the high elf Rodrick Marslett and asking &quot;where is fenn&quot; gives a response about how fenn was bailed out at the zero hour of his execution by none other than Lady McCabe herself.  Furthermore, Rodrick was told that if he ever escapes the dungeon, to go to the roof and find Fenn, who will guide him to safety.<BR>
<BR>
2:  Brollus Hoost no longer seems to be in kithicor since the haloween events.  A female NPC by the name of Tanlyn is in his place and says nothing about the quest at all.<BR>
<BR>
3:  PURE SPECULATION:  You follow the lead from Erudin to High Keep.  There you meet some NPC (unknown as of yet)who you question, and find out about Fenn Kaesick.  You go to the dungeons to find Fenn Keasick and ask jail clerk meryl about him when you can't find him.  she gives you the lead to Rodrick Marslett, his former cellmate.  this gives you the clue of where to find fenn (and in fact may be what causes him to spawn on the roof) as well as a lead to lady mccabe.  at this point i am stuck.  I figure that you ask Lady McCabe about fenn and she gives you a further lead to Brollus (or gives you a keyword that will trigger some response from fenn who then leads you to brollus).  from brollus you know to track down tallus to get the staff segment.  it must be either lady mccabe or fenn who tells you what to do with the segments bu i have yet to see this elusive lady.  If anyone knows how to get her to spawn i'd be thrilled.<BR>
<BR>
just my $0.02
				</font>
