				Alot of people seem to touch on the gambling table in high keep for this quest. I have an idea of how to actually play at the table. If you wait in the Bard guild near the gaming room a named female noble spawns, i can't recall her name. If you then follow her to the table, the npc who runs the table asks her if you are with her. She responds by saying she doesn't know you. I think you can play the table if you can convince this npc to vouch for you.
