				We seem to have lost our way a bit. I can assure you the two staff segments seem linked to the Quellious temple quest in Erudin. Please read my earlier posts. Here's a summary: Lumi Stergnon wants you to find out who stole a High Guard battlestaff. He doesn't appear to give you anything but gives you a lead, something to do with High pass. If you kill Tallus holton at a bandit camp in East kanara you get a segment and a High keep key)Tallus Holton is the former partner of Brollus Hoost(hangs around in kithicor). They were hired by Carson Mccabe (or Anna or Lady Mccabe) to get the staff, he is a weapons collector. Giving the staff segments to Lumi stergnon even with warm faction does not work. Talking to Carson does not seem to illicit a response. We are missing the next lead...are there more parts? <BR>
My friend suggested taking a boring erudite battlestaff and giving it to Carson, maybe he gives you the third piece. There is no clue as to why Tallus had the 2 pieces and didn't give them to Carson. Carson takes the 2 staff segments with a 'thanks' message ouch. Sorry i've had no luck getting any further. Maybe this summary will rejog someones memory.
